data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Halls! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence has been thoughtfully updated including two brand new HVAC units and a tankless water heater. The heart of the home features an open concept living area, ideal for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage, while the adjoining living room showcases a cozy fireplace.Each bedroom is generously sized and bathed in natural light, offering comfort and privacy for every member of your household. The master suite is a true retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom.Step outside to your backyard oasis, designed for outdoor enthusiasts and party hosts alike. The lush greenery and spacious patio create a perfect setting for dining and gatherings with family and friends.Located in a sought-after neighborhood and close to all amenities, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
